 its selection is inevitable,
 because it is indeed the better product of the two,
 and the selection of the better one was never in doubt.
 The process does not start with the thought that there is a 25% chance that I'll pick the shittier product.
 No;
 there is a 0% chance of that.
 It is fully and completely determined,
 with a 100% chance,
 that I will pick the better product.
