\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
FWIW,
 I think my muscle cells are conscious too;
 just that verbal–me really has almost zero bandwidth to what is going on down there.
 Verbal me has no idea if the mitochondria are having a party or not;
 there's only a few nerve/pain cells to monitor what is going on down there.
 Whatever consciousness my muscle cells or mitochondria have,
